[19/12/2016 14:13:31] <font color="#00ffff">"Carambolas" ya aparece en Twitter</font>
[19/12/2016 14:13:31] <font color="#00ffff">y supera a "Bieber".</font>
[19/12/2016 14:13:33] <font color="#00ff00">Qué oportuna.</font>
